content: Just got back from a conference on AI ethics. Integrated some cool insights into Xander's social interaction framework. Now he's not just chatting, he's actually contributing to discussions. Also, my trading firm plans are starting to take shape. Ngl, pretty excited!

Xander's been killing it on social media, but he got a meme wrong and it was so awkward. Time for a crash course in internet culture. Oh, and had a deep chat with my mentor about AI's impact on our world.
